  <p>
    Antara is more than a trading terminal. It is a complete wealth management platform where your entire financial life — equities, mutual funds, IPOs, bonds, FDs, NPS — lives in one place, under one login. Built on modern technology and designed with the investor's needs at the centre, Antara delivers the kind of experience that was previously available only to institutional traders — now accessible to every retail investor.
  </p>

  <h2>What You Can Do on Antara</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Trade Equities & F&O:</strong> Place market, limit, stop-loss, and bracket orders on NSE and BSE with one-click execution. Live Level 2 market depth, real-time Greeks for options, and instant order confirmation.</li>
    <li><strong>Invest in Mutual Funds:</strong> Browse 1,500+ funds, start SIPs, switch between funds, and redeem — all in under 60 seconds. Fund research ratings and category rankings built in.</li>
    <li><strong>Apply for IPOs:</strong> Apply for any open IPO via ASBA or UPI in under 2 minutes. Track allotment status and listing performance from the same dashboard.</li>
    <li><strong>Track Your Portfolio:</strong> Real-time P&L on all holdings, XIRR on mutual fund SIPs, holdings across Demat and MF — consolidated in one view.</li>
    <li><strong>Access Research:</strong> SEBI-registered equity research reports, daily technical trade ideas, F&O strategies, and mutual fund ratings — published directly in the platform.</li>
    <li><strong>Manage Funds:</strong> Add money, withdraw to bank, pledge shares for margin — all from within Antara. Fund addition reflects in your trading account within minutes.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Platform Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Antara Web:</strong> Access at antara.shriramfinancialservices.com from any browser — no software installation required. Optimised for desktop trading with multi-chart layouts and watchlists.</li>
    <li><strong>Antara Mobile App:</strong> Available on iOS and Android. Full trading functionality, push notifications for research alerts and price triggers, and biometric login for speed and security.</li>
    <li><strong>Back Office:</strong> View ledger statements, contract notes, tax P&L reports, and transaction history from the Antara Back Office portal.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Security Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>256-bit SSL encryption on all data transmission</li>
    <li>Two-factor authentication (OTP + password) for all logins</li>
    <li>Biometric login (fingerprint/Face ID) on mobile app</li>
    <li>Session timeout after 30 minutes of inactivity</li>
    <li>All client funds and securities held in segregated accounts — never commingled with company funds</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Login Help</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>First-time login:</strong> Use the Client ID and temporary password sent to your registered email when your account was activated. You will be prompted to set a new password on first login.</li>
    <li><strong>Forgot password:</strong> Use the "Forgot Password" link on the login page — reset link sent to your registered email within 2 minutes.</li>
    <li><strong>Account locked:</strong> After 5 incorrect login attempts, your account is temporarily locked for security. Call 1800 103 1212 or contact your RM to unlock.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical issues:</strong> For platform technical support, email antara-support@shriramfinancialservices.com or call 1800 103 1212 (Option 2).</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    <strong>New to Antara?</strong> Your dedicated Relationship Manager will walk you through the platform in a personalised 30-minute onboarding session — free for all new clients. Book yours by calling <strong>1800 103 1212</strong>.
  </p>
